      "html": "<h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Manganaro</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Manganaro also suggests: [Ἰου(?)]λία Σαλβίο[υ]</span></span></li></ul>"
