      "id": "commentary",
      "html": "<h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Manganaro notes that Albios is attested at Syracuse in IG XIV.70. Whether the text should be understood as relating to the original tomb is unclear. A second text is inscribed on one of the other walls (ISic003034)</p>  "
